#originalTopic=are-people-born-gay
The gene that controls sexuality has been found in fruit flies. A Google search for "fruit fly gay gene" will show you the article. We can toggle it on and off again.The proof is in twin studies and generational studies. It's probably not one gene, but that doesn't mean it's not a few recessive genes working together, or something similar. 